                "invention-title": [
                    "Pure oxygen combustion biomass boiler flue gas and carbon resource utilization system and method",
                    "纯氧燃烧生物质锅炉烟气及碳资源化利用系统和方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a pure oxygen combustion biomass boiler flue gas and carbon resource utilization system which comprises a water electrolysis mechanism, a boiler, an air supply mechanism and a carbon utilization mechanism. The first three-way valve divides flue gas at a flue gas outlet of the boiler into two parts, the first part of flue gas enters the dust remover, the dust remover, the cooler, the compression device and the cooler are sequentially connected, the cooler is connected with the liquid carbon dioxide storage tank, the second part of flue gas returns to a boiler hearth, and the primary air mechanism and the secondary air mechanism receive oxygen of the water electrolysis mechanism. The carbon utilization mechanism pressurizes hydrogen in the water electrolysis mechanism and carbon dioxide in the liquid carbon dioxide storage tank and then sends the hydrogen and the carbon dioxide into the methanol synthesis device to generate methanol. The pure oxygen combustion biomass boiler flue gas and carbon resource utilization system provided by the invention has the advantages of efficiently utilizing electrolytes, being low in carbon capture cost and improving the resource utilization rate."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开一种纯氧燃烧生物质锅炉烟气及碳资源化利用系统，纯氧燃烧生物质锅炉烟气及碳资源化利用系统包括电解水机构、锅炉、送风机构和碳利用机构，电解水机构制备得到氢气和氧气，第一三通阀将锅炉的烟气出口的烟气分成两部分，第一部分烟气进入除尘器，除尘器、降温器、压缩装置和冷却器依次相连，冷却器与液态二氧化碳储罐相连，第二部分烟气返回锅炉炉膛，一次风机构和二次风机构接收电解水机构的氧气，碳利用机构将电解水机构的氢气和液态二氧化碳储罐的二氧化碳加压后送入甲醇合成装置中生成甲醇。本发明提供的纯氧燃烧生物质锅炉烟气及碳资源化利用系统具备高效利用电解产物、碳捕集成本低、提高资源利用率的优点。"
                }
            ]
